tenberg-13-may/\">8.1</a>, <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/05/27/whats-new-in-gutenberg-27-may/\">8.2</a>, <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/06/11/whats-new-in-gutenberg-11-june/\">8.3</a>, <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/06/24/whats-new-in-gutenberg-24-june/\">8.4</a> et <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/08/whats-new-in-gutenberg-8-july/\">8.5</a>, mais aussi des correctifs et des am√©liorations de performance ayant √©t√© faits sur les versions <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/22/whats-new-in-gutenberg-july-22/\">8.6</a> et 8.7 de Gutenberg.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>L&rsquo;annonce de sortie de <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2020/07/wordpress-5-5-beta-1/\">WordPress 5.5 Beta 1 (en anglais)</a> met en √©vidence la plupart des nouvelles fonctionnalit√©s et am√©liorations de ces diff√©rentes versions de Gutenberg. Notons particuli√®rement l‚Äô√©dition en direct des images, la pr√©visualisation du rendu pour plusieurs appareils diff√©rents, le nouveau r√©pertoire de blocs et bien d&rsquo;autres am√©liorations pour une exp√©rience plus efficace et fluide.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-make-wordpress-core\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"NJGIg612tj\"><a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/30/block-api-updates-in-5-5/\">Block API Updates in 5.5</a></blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" title=\"&#8220;Block API Updates in 5.5&#8221; &#8212; Make WordPress Core\" src=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2020/07/30/block-api-updates-in-5-5/embed/#?secret=NJGIg612tj\" data-secret=\"NJGIg612tj\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-wordpress wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provid